      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=kagi.com&amp;sz=128\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 0.75em;padding:5px 10px;background:#f0f4f8;border-left:3px solid #7b9fc4;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.82em;color:#444;line-height:1.8;\">🌲 <a href=\"https://zirnhelt.github.io/super-rss-feed/review.html?url=https%3A%2F%2Fstallman.org%2Farchives%2F2026-mar-jun.html%2323_June_2026_%28Paying_for_climate_damage_under_proposed_UN_tax%29\" style=\"color:#7b9fc4;text-decoration:none;\">✏️</a></p>\n<img src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=kagi.com&amp;sz=128\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 0.75em;padding:5px 10px;background:#f0f4f8;border-left:3px solid #7b9fc4;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.82em;color:#444;line-height:1.8;\">🌲 <a href=\"https://zirnhelt.github.io/super-rss-feed/review.html?url=https%3A%2F%2Fstallman.org%2Farchives%2F2026-mar-jun.html%2323_June_2026_%28Paying_for_climate_damage_under_proposed_UN_tax%29\" style=\"color:#7b9fc4;text-decoration:none;\">✏️</a></p>\n<img src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=kagi.com&amp;sz=128\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=kagi.com&amp;sz=128\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p>\n\n  *Fossil fuel firms may have to pay for climate damage under <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2026/feb/01/fossil-fuel-firms-may-have-to-pay-for-climate-damage-under-proposed-un-tax\">proposed UN tax</a>.*\n</p>\n<p>\nThere is no chance they could afford to reimburse all the damage they\nare doing, but the tax might help save all of us if it pressures them\nto reduce the damage.\n</p>\n</li>",
